snippet.title: Amber Heard: Johnny Depp threw glass bottles at me “like grenades” | 5 News
snippet.description:
► Subscribe to 5 News: http://bit.ly/5NewsSub 

► Johnny Depp's ex-wife Amber Heard claimed he threw glass bottles at her "like grenades" in the latest testimony in Mr Depp’s libel trial. His lawyers say that is nonsense. It is all being aired in court because Mr Depp is suing The Sun newspaper over an article which called him a wife beater - something he denies.

► Amber Heard: 'I was Johnny Depp's punching bag'
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WDiEhCBVlN8

► #5News #News #JohnnyDepp
